---
@META
dir: src/app/auth
updated: 2026-03-18
files: 3
stack: Next.js 14, React 18, NextAuth, Zod

@EXPORTS
layout.tsx: AuthLayout — centered auth page layout (no nav)
signin/page.tsx: SignInPage — email/password login form with OAuth buttons
signup/page.tsx: SignUpPage — registration form (name, email, username, password)

@PROCESSES
SignIn: form submit → signIn("credentials") via next-auth/react → redirect to /chapters
SignUp: form submit → POST /api/auth/register → auto signIn → redirect to /onboarding

@DEPENDENCIES
internal: @/lib/validation-schemas (signInSchema, signUpSchema), @/components/ui
external: next-auth/react, next/navigation, zod
